{"tid":1758522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來琴日死左隻撐警曱甴","createTime":"2019-11-27T06:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T07:23:23.000Z","uid":81334,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1a24dfd451f2da5d444165214554fad122dc2839","tid":1758522,"uid":81334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"［撐警大聯盟召集人冼澤正逝世　李偲嫣撰文悼念］<br />\n<br />\n「撐警大聯盟」召集人、退休高級督察冼澤正因病離世，終年<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">64</span></span>歲。「撐警大聯盟」創辦人之一李偲嫣，在facebook證實消息。<br />\n<br />\n過去幾年的撐警活動中，均見到冼澤正和李偲嫣的身影，李偲嫣上載多張與冼澤正的合照悼念摯友。 <br />\n<br />\n哩隻曱甴係Facebook講六四係假 宜家就過唔到六十四歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ghxrfpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FghxrfpX.png&h=bb52d3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYjX6wF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYjX6wF.png&h=83de512c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2f58057778e6583d289f4b1ab4f8218807e1b7e","tid":1758522,"uid":8562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開心既"},{"pid":"3bea9fae6ef0aee6daf73a435de2c34187c2f221","tid":1758522,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658419a474bf20e759d3aa7752c8c74b71e2dab8","tid":1758522,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-